&lt;h1 id="when-you-truly-work-for-yourself"&gt;When You Truly Work for Yourself&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jul 26 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
